Shadow sides strategy is to corrupt and wound. I try to play my Sauron conditions early, to get the opponent add burdens. Also, I hope I can use my Wraith-World out with the Witch-King. The Scouts are there to be played with the WK to stop ARV. And when I get out FotR Enquea and Toldea with Nazgul Sword, and I spot 5 burdens, its goodbye to 2 companions.<br />
